      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "id": "55",
        "folderId": "40",
        "text": "Here are some other useful values. \"Balancing Huber and Quadratic\" looks like getting the following value to be as small as possible, and when that happens, I claim the next two values will be equal and will equal the worst case performance!"
      },
